And then add to that.

779
00:59:29,232 --> 00:59:32,657
你们到哪度假? 对什么过敏? 和谁有暧昧关系?
Where do you vacation? What are your allergies? Who'd you have an affair with?

780
00:59:32,819 --> 00:59:33,991
唯一的有效办法是...
The only way this works...

