The State Department insisted today that the crisis in Afghanistan...

791
01:00:35,215 --> 01:00:39,311
不会使美国转移在人质危机上的注意力
will not divert the attention of the United States from the plight of the hostages.

792
01:00:39,469 --> 01:00:42,188
被认为即便不是无能 至少也是勉强的...
