他们真的准备好了吗?
Are they even ready?

808
01:01:58,131 --> 01:01:59,383
他们快了
They're getting there.

809
01:01:59,549 --> 01:02:01,096
"进步最多"是没有奖励的
There's no prize for "Most improved."

810
01:02:01,259 --> 01:02:03,978
没得选 我不同意的话 军队就会在住处现身...
I don't have a choice. We say no, they show up at the residence...

811
01:02:04,137 --> 01:02:06,858
