You want us to go to the Grand Bazaar at 3:00 in the afternoon?

814
01:02:33,875 --> 01:02:36,879
你说给我们一天背熟假身份资料 然后直接去机场的
You said a day to learn our covers, then straight to the airport.

815
01:02:37,045 --> 01:02:38,672
他们怀疑什么了吗?
They suspect something?

816
01:02:38,838 --> 01:02:41,591
我知道的是 我们要假扮成一个电影剧组
What I know is, we need to pretend to be a movie crew.

817
