我们不去
We won't do it.

819
01:02:50,475 --> 01:02:53,194
他上报说摄制组还有六个人 所以他们会点人数
He told them that there were six of us. So they're expecting six.

820
01:02:53,353 --> 01:02:55,572
这时候还不现身的话 就可疑了
It would be suspicious not to show up at this point.

821
