该死 伙计们 我们还有别的选择吗?
God damn it, guys. What else do we have to do, all right?

822
01:02:58,024 --> 01:03:00,573
他是要暴露我们的底牌...
He's about to show them the only cards that we're holding...

823
01:03:00,735 --> 01:03:04,410
