01:03:04,572 --> 01:03:06,700
听着 我们没有其它选择了!
Look, we don't have any other choice!

825
01:03:06,866 --> 01:03:09,210
谁说我们能完全掌握自己的假身份?
Who says that we'll know our covers well enough?

826
01:03:09,369 --> 01:03:11,121
我们又不是中情局特工
We're not in the CIA.

827
01:03:12,247 --> 01:03:13,874
这是自杀
It's suicide.

828
01:03:14,040 --> 01:03:16,134
请你们相信我
I'm asking you to trust me.

829
01:03:17,544 --> 01:03:18,716
我不信你
I don't trust you.

830
01:03:21,256 --> 01:03:23,805
这就是游戏规则 乔 你生活在什么世界啊?
This is the game, Joe. What world are you living in?

831
01:03:23,967 --> 01:03:27,597
一个他们把人挂在吊车上的世界 鲍伯
The one where they're hanging people from construction cranes, Bob.

832
01:03:28,388 --> 01:03:30,857
太危险了 我不会带我妻子去集市的
It's too dangerous. I won't bring my wife into the bazaar.

833
01:03:32,934 --> 01:03:34,277
乔?
Joe?

834
01:03:40,984 --> 01:03:42,827
那我们两点见面
So we'll see you at 2.

835
01:04:05,675 --> 01:04:10,772
别太显眼 但看起来要和护照相片一样
So don't be recognizable but look exactly like your passport photo.

836
01:04:12,015 --> 01:04:14,484
我们婚礼之后 我还没这么紧张过
I haven't been this nervous since our wedding.

837
01:04:16,269 --> 01:04:18,363
希望这不是个大错
Only this isn't a huge mistake, hopefully.

838
01:04:19,814 --> 01:04:21,691
对不起 好了
Sorry. Okay.

839
